description: With his buddy's relationship on the skids, Princeton Price finally sees his opportunity to make his move on best friend, Elye Black. Elye thinks it's a little weird, but he's in a vulnerable place, and he reasons that maybe Princeton is onto something that he doesn't know about. He soon finds out that Princeton is onto something, into something, and about to cum all over something, as he shows Elye all the ins and outs of what he's been missing. By the time he's through, Elye won't even remember what's her name, or why he ever bothered in the first place. Enjoy!
title: Bustin' Buds
